collectible.name: CV Wearables: Avatars: Philosophical Investigation Pixel Owl
collectible.description: This owl was the founding member of the board of philosophical owls. She has been around since the time of the first pixels, and she also founded Alexandria's first library on CryptoVoxels. Appearances of her around the world are rare and silent. PI just answers philosophical questions. Created by The Philosopher. [NOT FOR SALE. Only transference for the members of the Philosophical Investigation Group]

collectible.name: The Book of Great Falls: Day Edition
collectible.description: This tome contains the near-full (80%) akashic records of Rye's late father. The Great Falls were his main meditation area and so a place where many ashes were scattered. The rocks of the falls date to the late Precambrian times and are about 750 million years old. The rocks are a resistant metamorphized schist, gneisses, metagraywackes, and metaconglomerates. Now a fallen king became a part of the Falls forever. This book wields all the good that Rye's father has done for himself and for others. This knowledge is important for the journey of joy and inspiration, but what page does your bookmark land on?
collectible.author: 0x5aaef3cc9c1fb5cb3e771f77979d08b3440f2674
